（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aa3c0bded327", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "306", "s": "0915", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "就業安全制度", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "islands", "civil_category": "勞工行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('islands-8b44517b-moex-00011', 'islands-8b44517b', 'islands-8b44517b-moex-114-1ffb5c63', 'sub-islands-8b44517b-03', NULL, 'essay', '我國人力結構隨著高齡化的加速，對長期照顧的需求迅速提升，除了有
效的運用國內的長照體系機構所提供的專業照護人力外，亦積極地開拓
引進外籍家庭看護工，以因應不足的照護人力需求。請針對我國當前移
工政策與長期照顧系統之間的關聯性，進行評估確認其具有的意義與價
值為何？（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aa3c0bded327", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "306", "s": "0915", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "就業安全制度", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "islands", "civil_category": "勞工行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('islands-8b44517b-moex-00012', 'islands-8b44517b', 'islands-8b44517b-moex-114-1ffb5c63', 'sub-islands-8b44517b-03', NULL, 'essay', '所謂就業安全制度係為建構就業服務、職業訓練、技能證照、人力資源
